    [Fileformat]

    1*              sal_uInt8       Pre-Tag (!= 0)
    1*              3-sal_uInt8     OffsetToEndOfRec in Bytes
    1*              sal_uInt8       Record-Type (==SFX_REC_TYPE_SINGLE)
    1*              sal_uInt8       Content-Version
    1*              sal_uInt16      Content-Tag
    SizeOfContent*  sal_uInt8       Content
*/
