    [Fileformat]

    1*                  sal_uInt8       Pre-Tag (==0)
    1*                  3-sal_uInt8     OffsetToEndOfRec in Bytes
    1*                  sal_uInt8       Record-Type (==SFX_REC_TYPE_FIXSIZE)
